The original Xata work implements PostgreSQL database branching using
Kubernetes VolumeSnapshots and the CloudNativePG operator. pg-branch
reimplements the branching concept as a standalone CLI tool using
PostgreSQL template databases, DDL event triggers, and three-way merge.

No source code was copied from the original Xata project. The branching
model, API surface, and implementation are original to pg-branch.
